以好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHehe"},{"pid":"8abb129b539da283e3a1158fd01028cd385eacef","tid":381241,"uid":17213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T20:21:24.000Z","msg":"人越大真係越痛苦  有時諗<br />\n究竟做一隻食物鏈最底層嘅老鼠開心d<br />\n定係做一個有思想嘅人會開心d<br />\n兩者分別就係一種註定上層口腹 無得反擊<br />\n人可以借自身微小能力去反擊壓逼者<br />\n諗到呢到  我諗我有答案"},{"pid":"f32f17eb0ecc952d141eeb0fbc1796f748571ef8","tid":381241,"uid":80662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T20:50:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人大左點解咁多野要煩？</blockquote><br />\n因為人大左會有貪念,如果唔貪,其實生活可以好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHehe</blockquote><br />\nhehe啫係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n由出世開始就咩都冇帶嚟架啦,<br />\n身邊所有野我都唔會睇得好重要.<br />\n但唔代表唔關心.只係盡力問心無愧<br />\n錢,愛情,友情,親情,都只係過眼雲煙.<br />\n物質上既野更加唔會追求,<br />\n留多一年o係香港之後就會做backpacker,<br />\n環遊見識呢個世界,之後已經死而無憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a486e7da333ef68db9b7eb91ade8395352154ec6","tid":381241,"uid":127396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T20:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2703a6a237073649de6a38c753732e0ba239fefb","tid":381241,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T23:55:53.000Z","msg":"我都覺得好攰 想死左佢"},{"pid":"08f8f7e35eba24284e384ff28731e9c63bda29e8","tid":381241,"uid":45238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:03:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人大左點解咁多野要煩？</blockquote><br />\n因為人大左會有貪念,如果唔貪,其實生活可以好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHehe</blockquote><br />\nhehe啫係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n由出世開始就咩都冇帶嚟架啦,<br />\n身邊所有野我都唔會睇得好重要.<br />\n但唔代表唔關心.只係盡力問心無愧<br 